nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A woman of Argentinian appearance, with full, red lips and a smile, stands on the left side of the frame in a vibrant, slightly blurry, nighttime club scene. She is clad in a pink, bulky, industrial-style mecha armor, made of metal and covering her body, and in her hands, she holds a huge black gun. To her right, a tall and powerfully built polar bear, also wearing identical mecha armor but in black, is dancing alongside her, its massive paws raised in the air, and its eyes directly facing the camera with a wide, cheerful grin spreading across its face. The setting is a crowded nightclub with people in the background, surrounded by smoke, and colorful lights flashing everywhere. The atmosphere is lively, with the woman and the polar bear seemingly lost in the music, moving in sync as if dancing together, their mecha armor glistening under the flashing lights.
